column5: What are some of the best options for bait in bulk coming from Baudett to Kenora. Looking for some good bait at a fair price. Thanks
skyline store on airport road in kenora 807-465-4000. some of the best prices around kenora
Thanks I will give them a try. Any other options would be great also.
Anglers pro shop in Nestor falls is great. Good pricing and we usually order ahead and have it waiting as we pass by. Give em a try. Always had good luck with them.
Anglers Pro in Nestor Falls is your best bet.
